---
const siteTitle = "Nathan Snyder";
const pageTitle = siteTitle;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Work on narrative, meaning, and coherence—how stories shape human life, institutions, and moral imagination over long time horizons."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <header class="site-header">
        <a class="site-title" href="/" aria-label="Home">{siteTitle}</a>
        <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <a href="/writing/">Writing</a>
          <a href="/about/">About</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <h1>
          I work on questions of narrative, meaning, and coherence—how stories
          shape human life, institutions, and moral imagination over long time
          horizons.
        </h1>

        <p>
          The writing here is concerned less with expression than with structure:
          how narratives hold, where they break, and what they make possible when
          they do. I publish slowly, revise deliberately, and favor work that
          remains intelligible even when context and fashion fall away.
        </p>

        <p>
          This site is not a feed. It is a record of thinking made public only
          when it feels settled enough to stand.
        </p>

        <div class="links">
          <a class="primary" href="/writing/">Writing →</a>
          <a class="secondary" href="/about/">About →</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <small>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {siteTitle}</small>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(html) {
    color-scheme: light;
  }

  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: ui-serif, Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  main {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem;
  }

  .site-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .site-title {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .site-title:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
  }

  .site-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .site-nav a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .site-nav a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 1.85rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hero p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .links {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
  }

  .primary {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .site-footer {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>